<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Horror_fiction&action=edit&section=11.php.html" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
